  <p>
    I'm Executive Director of the <a href="https://ocmeco.org">Open Commercial Media Ecosystem (OCME)</a>,
    a member-governed alternative to gatekeeper-controlled creator platforms.
  </p>

  <p>
    Background: BS Mechanical Engineering, PMP. I came up through engineering, product management,
    and smart-contract development before going full-time on OCME in August 2025.
  </p>

  <h2>Personal Mission</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>M1:</strong> Bring self-sovereign identity (SSI) technology to 100 million people by 2034.</li>
    <li><strong>M2:</strong> Develop decentralized systems that restore economic agency to creators and professionals.</li>
    <li><strong>M3:</strong> Build awareness of the transition to a new world view by creating accessible tools that help people thrive rather than just survive this transformation.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Global Problems I'm Working On</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>GP1:</strong> The lack of cryptographically secure, tamper-evident identity in digital technology has eroded trust.</li>
    <li><strong>GP2:</strong> The death of the old world creates unprecedented opportunity, but most people lack the tools and mindset to capitalize on the transformation rather than just survive it.</li>
    <li><strong>GP3:</strong> Upskilling is easier than ever, and more important than ever, yet wildly under-appreciated.</li>
  </ul>

